    "feat": {
        "name": "Interpose",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You put yourself between an ally and danger. Stride up to your Speed. You must end your movement adjacent to an ally. You and your ally then swap positions with each other. After changing positions, you can make a melee Strike against an enemy within your reach.",
